title: BobbyCast #68 with Kip Moore
itunes:title: BobbyCast #68 with Kip Moore
description:
Kip Moore stops by the house.  Kip talks about his new music and how it’s different than anything he’s ever done. Kip also talks about his a live shows, up and downs of his career and shares some ghost stories. Subscribe to the BobbyCast for more episodes!
